### Search Foods and Combos by Name - Tìm kiếm Food và Combo theo tên
GET {{host}}/api/food/search-foods-and-combos?name=bánh mì
Content-Type: application/json

### Search with different keywords
GET {{host}}/api/food/search-foods-and-combos?name=combo
Content-Type: application/json

### Search with partial name
GET {{host}}/api/food/search-foods-and-combos?name=bánh
Content-Type: application/json

### Search with single character
GET {{host}}/api/food/search-foods-and-combos?name=c
Content-Type: application/json

### Search with no results (test case)
GET {{host}}/api/food/search-foods-and-combos?name=xyz123
Content-Type: application/json

### Search without name parameter (should return all)
GET {{host}}/api/food/search-foods-and-combos
Content-Type: application/json

### Search with empty name parameter (should return all)
GET {{host}}/api/food/search-foods-and-combos?name=
Content-Type: application/json

### Search with whitespace only (should return all)
GET {{host}}/api/food/search-foods-and-combos?name=%20%20%20
Content-Type: application/json

### Search case insensitive test
GET {{host}}/api/food/search-foods-and-combos?name=BÁNH MÌ
Content-Type: application/json

### Compare with get all endpoint
GET {{host}}/api/food/all-foods-and-combos
Content-Type: application/json

### Variables
@host = https://localhost:7001